### 使用说明 / Notes
### 1. 先运行“登录管理员”和“登录普通用户”接口。
### 2. 从返回结果 data.token 里复制 token。
### 3. 把 token 粘贴到下面的 adminToken / userToken。
### 4. 再测试 /me 和 /admin/** 接口。

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken = paste_admin_token_here
@userToken = paste_user_token_here


### 01 注册用户 / Register user
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "spring01",
  "password": "123456"
}


### 02 登录普通用户 alice，获取 USER token / Login as normal user
POST  http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "abc123"
}


### 03 登录管理员 tom，获取 ADMIN token / Login as admin
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "tom",
  "password": "123456"
}


### 04 不带 token 访问 /me，应该失败 / Access /me without token
GET {{baseUrl}}/me


### 05 使用错误 token 访问 /me，应该失败 / Access /me with invalid token
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: invalid-token


### 06 普通用户查看自己的信息 / USER access /me
GET http://localhost:8080/me
Authorization: c9409153-bf8b-4f10-be3c-2c3a73b687c9


### 07 普通用户修改自己的密码 / USER change own password
PUT {{baseUrl}}/me/password
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "abcdef"
}


### 08 使用新密码登录普通用户 / Login with new password
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "abcdef"
}


### 09 把普通用户密码改回 abc123 / Change user password back
### 如果刚刚运行了 08，请先把 08 返回的新 token 复制到 userToken。
PUT {{baseUrl}}/me/password
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "abc123"
}


### 10 USER token 访问管理员接口，应该失败 / USER access admin API should fail
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: {{userToken}}


### 11 管理员查询全部用户 / ADMIN get all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: {{adminToken}}


### 12 管理员查询单个用户 / ADMIN get one user
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/alice
Authorization: {{adminToken}}


### 13 管理员重置用户密码 / ADMIN reset user password
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/alice/password
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "abcdef"
}


### 14 管理员删除用户 / ADMIN delete user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/spring01
Authorization: {{adminToken}}


### 15 参数校验失败：用户名为空，密码太短 / Validation error
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "password": "123"
}

### 退出登录 / Logout
POST http://localhost:8080/logout
Authorization: c9409153-bf8b-4f10-be3c-2c3a73b687c9


