### =========================
### 收支记录模块 / Transaction records
### 使用前：
### 1. 先登录普通用户，复制 token 到文件顶部的 @userToken。
### 2. 先创建分类，再查询分类，确认 categoryId。
### 3. 下面的 categoryId 要换成当前用户自己的分类 id。
### =========================


### 01 新增支出记录 / Add expense record
POST http://localhost:8080/transaction-records
Authorization: f1b3d327-5914-498d-b654-90986bcf817a
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 2,
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 1200.50,
  "remark": "午饭",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-23"
}


### 02 新增收入记录 / Add income record
POST {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records
Authorization: f1b3d327-5914-498d-b654-90986bcf817a
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 3,
  "type": "income",
  "amount": 200000,
  "remark": "工资",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-23"
}


### 03 查询自己的全部收支记录 / Get my records
GET {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records
Authorization: f1b3d327-5914-498d-b654-90986bcf817a


### 04 按类型查询支出记录 / Get my expense records
GET {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records/type/expense
Authorization: f1b3d327-5914-498d-b654-90986bcf817a


### 05 按类型查询收入记录 / Get my income records
GET {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records/type/income
Authorization: f1b3d327-5914-498d-b654-90986bcf817a


### 06 按日期范围查询记录 / Get my records by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records/range?startRecordDate=2026-06-01&endOfRecordDate=2026-06-30
Authorization: f1b3d327-5914-498d-b654-90986bcf817a


### 07 修改自己的收支记录 / Update my record
### 把路径里的 1 换成自己的 record id。
PUT {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records/1
Authorization: f1b3d327-5914-498d-b654-90986bcf817a
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 2,
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 1500,
  "remark": "晚饭",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-23"
}


### 08 删除自己的收支记录 / Delete my record
### 把路径里的 1 换成自己的 record id。
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records/1
Authorization: f1b3d327-5914-498d-b654-90986bcf817a


### 09 不带 token 新增记录，应该失败 / Add record without token should fail
POST {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 2,
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 1200,
  "remark": "没有token",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-23"
}


### 10 分类 id 不存在，应该失败 / Category id not found should fail
POST {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records
Authorization: f1b3d327-5914-498d-b654-90986bcf817a
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 9999,
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 1200,
  "remark": "不存在的分类",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-23"
}


### 11 类型和分类类型不一致，应该失败 / Record type and category type mismatch should fail
### 例如 categoryId 是支出分类，但 type 写 income。
POST {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records
Authorization: f1b3d327-5914-498d-b654-90986bcf817a
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 2,
  "type": "income",
  "amount": 1200,
  "remark": "类型不一致",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-23"
}


### 12 金额为 0，应该失败 / Amount zero should fail
POST {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records
Authorization: f1b3d327-5914-498d-b654-90986bcf817a
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 2,
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 0,
  "remark": "金额为0",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-23"
}


### 13 日期范围错误，应该失败 / Invalid date range should fail
GET {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records/range?startRecordDate=2026-06-30&endOfRecordDate=2026-06-01
Authorization: f1b3d327-5914-498d-b654-90986bcf817a


### =========================
### Alice 空数据完整流程测试 / Alice full flow
### 使用方法：
### 1. 先运行 A01，复制返回的 data.token。
### 2. 粘贴到文件顶部 @userToken = 后面。
### 3. 按 A02 -> A03 -> A04 的顺序创建并查询分类。
### 4. 把 A06 / A07 / A12 / A15 里的 categoryId 换成 A04 返回的真实分类 id。
### 5. A08 查询记录后，把 A12 / A13 路径里的记录 id 换成真实记录 id。
### =========================


### A01 登录 alice，获取 token / Login alice and get token
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "abc123"
}


### A02 新增 alice 的支出分类：餐饮 / Add alice expense category
POST http://localhost:8080/transaction-categories
Authorization: 650e7e62-fe54-4785-841a-0587a85263cf
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "餐饮",
  "type": "expense"
}


### A03 新增 alice 的收入分类：工资 / Add alice income category
POST http://localhost:8080/transaction-categories
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "工资",
  "type": "income"
}


### A04 查询 alice 自己的分类，确认分类 id / Get alice categories and check ids
GET http://localhost:8080/transaction-categories
Authorization: 2955b25f-64e2-4e7c-9bf9-a8183dee2e6f


### A05 分类类型错误，应该失败 / Add category with invalid type should fail
POST http://localhost:8080/transaction-categories
Authorization: 650e7e62-fe54-4785-841a-0587a85263cf
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "乱写分类",
  "type": "abc"
}


### A06 新增 alice 的支出记录 / Add alice expense record
### 把 categoryId 换成 A04 返回的“餐饮”分类 id。
POST http://localhost:8080/transaction-records
Authorization: 650e7e62-fe54-4785-841a-0587a85263cf
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 3,
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 1200.50,
  "remark": "午饭",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-23"
}


### A07 新增 alice 的收入记录 / Add alice income record
### 把 categoryId 换成 A04 返回的“工资”分类 id。
POST http://localhost:8080/transaction-records
Authorization: 650e7e62-fe54-4785-841a-0587a85263cf
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 3,
  "type": "income",
  "amount": 200000,
  "remark": "工资",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-23"
}


### A08 查询 alice 自己的全部收支记录 / Get alice records
GET http://localhost:8080/transaction-records
Authorization: 650e7e62-fe54-4785-841a-0587a85263cf


### A09 按类型查询 alice 的支出记录 / Get alice expense records
GET http://localhost:8080/transaction-records/type/expense
Authorization: 650e7e62-fe54-4785-841a-0587a85263cf


### A10 按类型查询 alice 的收入记录 / Get alice income records
GET http://localhost:8080/transaction-records/type/income
Authorization: 650e7e62-fe54-4785-841a-0587a85263cf


### A11 按日期范围查询 alice 的记录 / Get alice records by date range
GET http://localhost:8080/transaction-records/range?startRecordDate=2026-06-01&endOfRecordDate=2026-06-30
Authorization: 650e7e62-fe54-4785-841a-0587a85263cf


### A12 修改 alice 自己的收支记录 / Update alice record
### 把路径里的 1 换成 A08 返回的真实记录 id。
### categoryId 也要换成 A04 返回的、属于 alice 的分类 id。
PUT http://localhost:8080/transaction-records/1
Authorization: 650e7e62-fe54-4785-841a-0587a85263cf
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 3,
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 1500,
  "remark": "晚饭",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-23"
}


### A13 删除 alice 自己的收支记录 / Delete alice record
### 把路径里的 1 换成 A08 返回的真实记录 id。
DELETE http://localhost:8080/transaction-records/2
Authorization: 650e7e62-fe54-4785-841a-0587a85263cf


### A14 使用不存在的分类 id 新增记录，应该失败 / Add record with invalid category id should fail
POST http://localhost:8080/transaction-records
Authorization: 650e7e62-fe54-4785-841a-0587a85263cf
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 9999,
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 1000,
  "remark": "不存在的分类",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-23"
}


### A15 类型和分类类型不一致，应该失败 / Type mismatch should fail
### 例如 categoryId 是“餐饮 expense”，但 type 写成 income。
POST http://localhost:8080/transaction-records
Authorization:650e7e62-fe54-4785-841a-0587a85263cf
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 3,
  "type": "income",
  "amount": 1000,
  "remark": "类型不一致",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-23"
}


### A16 日期范围错误，应该失败 / Invalid date range should fail
GET http://localhost:8080/transaction-records/range?startRecordDate=2026-06-30&endOfRecordDate=2026-06-01
Authorization: 650e7e62-fe54-4785-841a-0587a85263cf

